#. §0: `h2`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L02_Forward
msgid "Now use §0 to prove the goal."
msgstr "现在使用 §0 来证明目标。"

#: Game
msgid "# Glimpse of Lean\n"
"\n"
"Welcome to this tutorial designed to give you a glimpse of Lean.\n"
"\n"
"This game is split into **Worlds**. Each world focuses on a specific aspect of Lean.\n"
"\n"
"*   **Computing**: Learn how to calculate and rewrite equalities.\n"
"*   **Logic**: Learn how to handle logical implications and quantifiers.\n"
"\n"
"Start with the **Computing** world to learn the basics."
msgstr "# Lean 初探\n"
"\n"
"欢迎来到本教程，它旨在让你在几小时内对 Lean 有一个初步的了解。\n"
"\n"
"本游戏分为多个 **世界**。每个世界都专注于 Lean 的特定方面。\n"
"\n"
"*   **计算**：学习如何计算和重写等式。\n"
"*   **逻辑**：学习如何处理逻辑蕴含和量词。\n"
"\n"
"请从 **计算** 世界开始学习基础知识。"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "intermediate goal solved! 🎉"
msgstr "中间目标已解决！🎉"

#. §0: `exact`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L01_Implications
msgid "You can use §0 to provide the proof term directly."
msgstr "你可以使用 §0 直接提供证明项。"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L06_RwReverse
msgid "Rewriting from right to left"
msgstr "从右向左重写"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L04_RwMultiple
msgid "Good job! You can combine rewrites."
msgstr "干得好！你可以组合重写。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L01_Implications
msgid "Using implications"
msgstr "使用蕴含"

#: Game
msgid "Glimpse to Game"
msgstr "Lean 初探游戏"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `:=`
#. §2: `by`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L07_Calc
msgid "What is written in the above example is very far away from what we would write on\n"
"paper. Let's now see how to get a more natural layout (and also return to using §0\n"
"instead of explicit lemma invocations).\n"
"After each §1 below, the goal is to prove equality with the preceding line\n"
"(or the left-hand on the first line).\n"
"Carefully check you understand this by putting your cursor after each §2 and looking\n"
"at the tactic state."
msgstr "上面的例子与我们在纸上书写的形式相去甚远。现在让我们看看如何获得更自然的布局（并重新使用 §0\n"
"而不是显式引理调用）。\n"
"在下面的每个 §1 之后，目标是证明与前一行（或第一行的左侧）相等。\n"
"通过将光标放在每个 §2 之后并查看策略状态，仔细检查你是否理解了这一点。"

#. §0: `have`
#. §1: `have my_name : my_statement := by`
#. §2: `my_name`
#. §3: `exact`
#. §4: `by`
#. §5: `exact`
#. §6: `exact`
#. §7: `:=`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L02_Forward
msgid "You can also give a proof with forward reasoning, using the §0 tactic.\n"
"In order to announce an intermediate statement we use:\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"and then increase the indentation level.\n"
"This triggers the apparition of a new goal: proving the statement.\n"
"After the proof is done, the statement becomes available under the name §2.\n"
"If the proof is a single §3 tactic then you can get rid\n"
"of §4 and §5 and directly put the argument of §6 after the §7."
msgstr "你也可以使用 §0 策略进行前向推理来给出证明。\n"
"为了声明一个中间陈述，我们使用：\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"然后增加缩进级别。\n"
"这将触发一个新目标的出现：证明该陈述。\n"
"证明完成后，该陈述将以名称 §2 可用。\n"
"如果证明只是一个 §3 策略，那么你可以去掉\n"
"§4 和 §5，直接将 §6 的参数放在 §7 之后。"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "level completed with warnings… 🎭"
msgstr "关卡已完成，但有警告… 🎭"

#. §0: `exp`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Correct! You used lemmas about §0 to rewrite the goal."
msgstr "正确！你使用了关于 §0 的引理来重写目标。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L02_Expansion
msgid "Correct! §0 handles expansions too."
msgstr "正确！§0 也可以处理展开。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic
msgid "Logic"
msgstr "逻辑"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "Now finish with §0."
msgstr "现在用 §0 完成。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L01_Associativity
msgid "Great! The §0 tactic handles basic algebraic identities."
msgstr "太棒了！§0 策略可以处理基本的代数恒等式。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L02_Forward
msgid "Forward Reasoning"
msgstr "前向推理"

#. §0: `b`
#. §1: `«{h'}»`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "Note the goal changed. Now rewrite §0 using §1."
msgstr "注意目标改变了。现在使用 §1 重写 §0。"

#. §0: `intro`
#. §1: `a > 0 → (a^2)^2 > 0`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L03_ProvingImplications
msgid "In order to prove an implication, we need to assume the premise and prove the conclusion.\n"
"This is done using the §0 tactic. Secretly the exercise above was proving the\n"
"implication §1 but the premise was already introduced for us."
msgstr "为了证明一个蕴含，我们需要假设前提并证明结论。\n"
"这是使用 §0 策略完成的。实际上，上面的练习是在证明\n"
"蕴含 §1，但前提已经为我们引入了。"

#. §0: `P ⇒ Q`
#. §1: `P`
#. §2: `Q`
#. §3: `→`
#. §4: `⇒`
#. §5: `a`
#. §6: `sq_pos_of_pos`
#. §7: `0 < a → 0 < a^2`
#. §8: `sq_pos_of_pos`
#. §9: `ha`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L01_Implications
msgid "# Implications\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, the inhabitants of a proposition are precisely the proofs of that proposition.\n"
"Proving an implication §0 amounts to producing a function that turns proofs of §1\n"
"into proofs of §2. Therefore, Lean denotes implication by the symbol §3 instead of §4.\n"
"\n"
"For instance, given a real number §5, the lemma §6 claims §7\n"
"so the proof belows apply the \"function\" §8 to the assumption §9."
msgstr "# 蕴含\n"
"\n"
"在 Lean 中，命题的居民正是该命题的证明。\n"
"证明蕴含 §0 相当于产生一个函数，将 §1 的证明转换为 §2 的证明。因此，Lean 用符号 §3 而不是 §4 来表示蕴含。\n"
"\n"
"例如，给定一个实数 §5，引理 §6 声称 §7\n"
"所以下面的证明将“函数” §8 应用于假设 §9。"

#. §0: `rw`
#. §1: `b + c + e = d + c`
#. §2: `a + e = d + c`
#. §3: `h`
#. §4: `a = b + c`
#. §5: `b + c + e = d + c`
#. §6: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "Note the §0 tactic changes the current goal. After the first line of the above proof,\n"
"the new goal is §1. So you can read this first proof step as saying:\n"
"\"I wanted to prove, §2 but, since assumption §3 tells me §4,\n"
"it suffices to prove §5.\"\n"
"\n"
"The §6 tactic needs to be told every rewrite step. Later on we will see more powerful tactics\n"
"that can automate the tedious steps for you."
msgstr "注意 §0 策略改变了当前目标。在上述证明的第一行之后，\n"
"新目标是 §1。所以你可以将这第一步证明理解为：\n"
"“我想证明 §2，但是，因为假设 §3 告诉我 §4，\n"
"所以只需证明 §5。”\n"
"\n"
"§6 策略需要被告知每一个重写步骤。稍后我们将看到更强大的策略，\n"
"可以为你自动完成这些繁琐的步骤。"

#: Game
msgid "Based on the [Glimpse of Lean](https://github.com/PatrickMassot/GlimpseOfLean) tutorial."
msgstr "基于 [Glimpse of Lean](https://github.com/PatrickMassot/GlimpseOfLean) 教程。"

#. §0: `←`
#. §1: `rw [← h]`
#. §2: `b + c`
#. §3: `a`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L06_RwReverse
msgid "Since equality is a symmetric relation, we can also replace the right-hand side of an\n"
"equality by the left-hand side using §0 as in the following example.\n"
"\n"
"Whenever you see in a Lean file a symbol that you don't see on your keyboard, such as ←,\n"
"you can put your mouse cursor above it and learn from a tooltip how to type it.\n"
"In the case of ←, you can type it by typing \"\\\\l \", so backslash-l-space.\n"
"\n"
"Note this rewriting from right to left story is all about sides in the equality you want to\n"
"*use*, not about sides in what you want to *prove*. The §1 in the previous example\n"
"replaced the right-hand side by the left-hand side, so it looked for §2 in the current\n"
"goal and replaced it with §3."
msgstr "由于等号是对称关系，我们也可以像下面的例子一样，使用 §0 将等号的右边替换为左边。\n"
"\n"
"每当你在 Lean 文件中看到键盘上没有的符号（如 ←）时，\n"
"你可以将鼠标光标放在它上面，通过提示了解如何输入它。\n"
"对于 ←，你可以输入 \"\\\\l \"，即反斜杠-l-空格。\n"
"\n"
"注意，这个从右向左重写的故事完全是关于你想要 *使用* 的等式的两边，而不是关于你想要 *证明* 的两边。上例中的 §1\n"
"将右边替换为左边，所以它在当前目标中寻找 §2 并将其替换为 §3。"

#. §0: `a`
#. §1: `«{h}»`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "Start by rewriting §0 using §1."
msgstr "首先使用 §1 重写 §0。"

#: Game
msgid "Game Template"
msgstr "游戏模板"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `exp_add x y`
#. §2: `exp(x+y) = exp(x) * exp(y)`
#. §3: `exp_sub x y`
#. §4: `exp(x-y) = exp(x) / exp(y)`
#. §5: `exp_zero`
#. §6: `exp 0 = 1`
#. §7: `a + b - c`
#. §8: `(a + b) - c`
#. §9: `ring`
#. §10: `mul_one x : x * 1 = x`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "In the previous examples, we rewrote the goal using a local assumption. But we can\n"
"also use lemmas. For instance let us prove a lemma about exponentiation.\n"
"Since §0 only knows how to prove things from the axioms of rings,\n"
"it doesn't know how to work with exponentiation.\n"
"\n"
"§1 is a proof that §2.\n"
"§3 is §4.\n"
"§5 is §6.\n"
"\n"
"Recall that §7 means §8.\n"
"\n"
"You can either use §9 or rewrite with §10 to simplify the denominator on the\n"
"right-hand side."
msgstr "在前面的例子中，我们使用局部假设重写了目标。但我们也可以使用引理。\n"
"例如，让我们证明一个关于幂运算的引理。\n"
"因为 §0 只知道如何从环公理证明事物，\n"
"它不知道如何处理幂运算。\n"
"\n"
"§1 是 §2 的证明。\n"
"§3 是 §4。\n"
"§5 是 §6。\n"
"\n"
"回想一下，§7 意味着 §8。\n"
"\n"
"你可以使用 §9 或用 §10 重写来简化右边的分母。"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L07_Calc
msgid "Calculation layout using calc"
msgstr "使用 calc 进行计算布局"

#. §0: `rw`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "Let us now see how to compute using assumptions relating the involved numbers.\n"
"This uses the fundamental property of equality: if two\n"
"mathematical objects A and B are equal then, in any statement involving A, one can replace A\n"
"by B. This operation is called rewriting, and the basic Lean tactic for this is §0.\n"
"Carefully step through the proof below and try to understand what is happening."
msgstr "现在让我们看看如何使用涉及相关数字的假设进行计算。\n"
"这利用了等式的基本性质：如果两个数学对象 A 和 B 相等，那么在任何涉及 A 的陈述中，都可以用 B 替换 A。\n"
"这种操作称为重写，Lean 中用于此操作的基本策略是 §0。\n"
"仔细逐步阅读下面的证明，尝试理解发生了什么。"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L03_RwBasic
msgid "The rewriting tactic"
msgstr "重写策略"

#. §0: `«{h'}»`
#. §1: `c`
#. §2: `b`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L06_RwReverse
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L06_RwReverse
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L06_RwReverse
msgid "Use §0 to replace §1 with §2."
msgstr "使用 §0 将 §1 替换为 §2。"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L04_RwMultiple
msgid "Multiple rewrites"
msgstr "多次重写"

#: GameServer.RpcHandlers
msgid "level completed! 🎉"
msgstr "关卡完成！🎉"

#. §0: `→`
#. §1: `↔`
#. §2: `∀`
#. §3: `∃`
#: Game.Levels.Logic
msgid "# Logic\n"
"\n"
"## Implications and Quantifiers\n"
"\n"
"In this world, we will learn how to handle logical implications (§0), equivalences (§1),\n"
"and quantifiers (§2, §3)."
msgstr "# 逻辑\n"
"\n"
"## 蕴含与量词\n"
"\n"
"在这个世界中，我们将学习如何处理逻辑蕴含 (§0)、等价 (§1) 和量词 (§2, §3)。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L02_Expansion
msgid "Use §0 to prove algebraic identities."
msgstr "使用 §0 来证明代数恒等式。"

#. §0: `intro`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L03_ProvingImplications
msgid "Note that, when using §0, you need to give a name to the assumption.\n"
"Lean will let you use a name that was already used, but the safe\n"
"thing to do by default is to use a new name."
msgstr "注意，当使用 §0 时，你需要给假设一个名字。\n"
"Lean 允许你使用已经使用过的名字，但默认情况下，\n"
"为了安全起见，最好使用一个新名字。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `ring`
#. §2: `a*b*c`
#. §3: `(a*b)*c`
#. §4: `a*(b*c)`
#. §5: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L02_Expansion
msgid "It's your turn, replace the word sorry below by a proof. In this case the proof is just §0.\n"
"After you prove something, you will see a small \"No goals\" message, which is the indication that\n"
"your proof is finished.\n"
"\n"
"In the previous example, take a closer look at where Lean displays parentheses.\n"
"The §1 tactic certainly knows about associativity of multiplication, but sometimes\n"
"it is useful to understand that binary operation really are binary and an expression like\n"
"§2 is read as §3 by Lean and the fact that this is equal to §4 is a\n"
"lemma that is used by the §5 tactic when needed."
msgstr "轮到你了，将下面的 sorry 替换为证明。在这种情况下，证明就是 §0。\n"
"在你证明了一些东西之后，你会看到一条小小的“无目标”消息，这表明你的证明完成了。\n"
"\n"
"在前面的例子中，仔细看看 Lean 在哪里显示括号。\n"
"§1 策略当然知道乘法的结合律，但有时理解二元运算确实是二元的很有用，\n"
"像 §2 这样的表达式被 Lean 读作 §3，而它等于 §4 这一事实是 §5 策略在需要时使用的引理。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L03_ProvingImplications
msgid "Proving Implications"
msgstr "证明蕴含"

#. §0: `exp (a + b)`
#. §1: `exp_add`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Now expand §0 using §1."
msgstr "现在使用 §1 展开 §0。"

#. §0: `intro`
#. §1: `ha`
#. §2: `a > 0`
#. §3: `hb`
#. §4: `b > 0`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L03_ProvingImplications
msgid "Use §0 to bring the assumptions §1 (for §2) and §3 (for §4) into the context."
msgstr "使用 §0 将假设 §1（对应 §2）和 §3（对应 §4）引入上下文中。"

#. §0: `rw [h, h']`
#. §1: `h`
#. §2: `h'`
#. §3: `ring`
#. §4: `h`
#. §5: `h'`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L04_RwMultiple
msgid "One can actually do several rewritings in one command.\n"
"§0 rewrites §1 then §2.\n"
"\n"
"Now try it yourself. Note that §3 can still do calculations,\n"
"but it doesn't use the assumptions §4 and §5."
msgstr "实际上可以在一条命令中进行多次重写。\n"
"§0 先重写 §1，然后重写 §2。\n"
"\n"
"现在你自己试试。注意 §3 仍然可以进行计算，\n"
"但它不使用假设 §4 和 §5。"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `mul_one`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Now verify the equality with §0 or §1."
msgstr "现在用 §0 或 §1 验证等式。"

#. §0: `have h2 : 0 < a^2`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L02_Forward
msgid "Start by declaring §0."
msgstr "首先声明 §0。"

#: Game.Levels.Logic.L02_Forward
msgid "Forward reasoning allows you to build up intermediate facts to reach your goal."
msgstr "前向推理允许你建立中间事实来达成目标。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L04_RwMultiple
msgid "Now verify the equality with §0."
msgstr "现在用 §0 验证等式。"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting
msgid "Computing"
msgstr "计算"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L02_Expansion
msgid "Expansion"
msgstr "展开"

#. §0: `ring`
#. §1: `rw`
#. §2: `exact`
#. §3: `calc`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L07_Calc
msgid "Congratulations, this is the end of your first exercise file! You've seen what typing\n"
"a Lean proof looks like and have learned about the following tactics:\n"
"* §0\n"
"* §1\n"
"* §2\n"
"* §3"
msgstr "恭喜，这是你第一个练习文件的结束！你已经看到了输入 Lean 证明是什么样子的，\n"
"并学习了以下策略：\n"
"* §0\n"
"* §1\n"
"* §2\n"
"* §3"

#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Rewriting with a lemma"
msgstr "使用引理重写"

#. §0: `add_pos`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L03_ProvingImplications
msgid "Now use §0 with your new assumptions."
msgstr "现在使用 §0 和你的新假设。"

#: Game
msgid "You should use this game as a template for your own game and add your own levels."
msgstr "你应该使用此游戏作为你自己游戏的模板，并添加你自己的关卡。"

#. §0: `0 < a`
#: Game.Levels.Logic.L01_Implications
msgid "The above proof is a direct proof: we already know §0 and we feed this fact into the\n"
"implication."
msgstr "上面的证明是直接证明：我们已经知道 §0，我们将这个事实输入到蕴含中。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting
msgid "# Computing\n"
"\n"
"## The ring tactic\n"
"\n"
"One of the earliest kind of proofs one encounters while learning mathematics is proving by\n"
"a calculation. It may not sound like a proof, but this is actually using lemmas expressing\n"
"properties of operations on numbers. Of course we usually don't want to invoke those explicitly\n"
"so mathlib has a tactic §0 taking care of proving equalities that follow by applying\n"
"the properties of all commutative rings."
msgstr "# 计算\n"
"\n"
"## ring 策略\n"
"\n"
"学习数学时最早遇到的证明之一是通过计算进行证明。这听起来可能不像证明，但实际上这是在使用表达数运算性质的引理。当然，我们通常不想显式调用这些引理，所以 mathlib 有一个策略 §0，它负责通过应用所有交换环的性质来证明等式。"

#. §0: `«{h}»`
#. §1: `«{h'}»`
#. §2: `rw [«{h}», «{h'}»]`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L04_RwMultiple
msgid "Try rewriting both §0 and §1. You can do it in one command §2 or two."
msgstr "尝试重写 §0 和 §1。你可以在一个命令 §2 中完成，也可以分两次完成。"

#. §0: `exp (a + b - c)`
#. §1: `exp_sub`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Start by expanding §0 using §1."
msgstr "首先使用 §1 展开 §0。"

#. §0: `exp 0`
#. §1: `exp_zero`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L05_RwLemma
msgid "Simplify §0 using §1."
msgstr "使用 §1 简化 §0。"

#. §0: `ring`
#: Game.Levels.Rewriting.L01_Associativity
msgid "One of the earliest kind of proofs one encounters while learning mathematics is proving by\n"
"a calculation. It may not sound like a proof, but this is actually using lemmas expressing\n"
"properties of operations on numbers. Of course we usually don't want to invoke those explicitly\n"
"so mathlib has a tactic §0 taking care of proving equalities that follow by applying\n"
"the properties of all commutative rings."
msgstr "学习数学时最早遇到的证明之一是通过计算进行证明。这听起来可能不像证明，但实际上这是在使用表达数运算性质的引理。当然，我们通常不想显式调用这些引理，所以 mathlib 有一个策略 §0，它负责通过应用所有交换环的性质来证明等式。"

#. §0: `0 < a^2`
#. §1: `sq_pos_of_pos`
